{"tid":2047703,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［限聚令］9月中之前都唔洗諗去外國旅行啦","createTime":"2020-06-02T09:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T03:56:26.000Z","uid":91407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"367bc26cb95e0b616ff3d88aba07118c863024dc","tid":2047703,"uid":91407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"source from 蘋果<br />\n<br />\n限聚令及食肆禁令會再延長14日至本月18日。<br />\n<br />\n至於口岸管制方面，延長內地、澳門和台灣抵港人士要接受強制檢疫的規例多一個月，至下月7日，並有限度、有條件放寬從粵澳來港人士；<em>延長海外抵港人士接受強制檢疫的規例多3個月，至9月18日</em>。<br />\n<br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n【限聚令食肆禁令延長兩周至6.18　擬放寬粵澳人士來港】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3coPs6P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3coPs6P&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=56365a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3coPs6P</a><br />\n【祿泉樓再有女居民不適抱B送院　居民憂病毒大爆發搬走避疫】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2U4bIg2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2U4bIg2&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=79e18b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2U4bIg2</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🌎《蘋果》英文版現已上架<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XLjbRZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XLjbRZ&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=7a5c6c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XLjbRZ</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🍎 黎智英：經營非常困難 請支持訂閱<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VLuV6g&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=530083d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VLuV6g</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🕯「六四‧三一」──守住歷史 拒絕遺忘<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Xg3SSj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Xg3SSj&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=7287352d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Xg3SSj</a>"},{"pid":"ab4c021c125d2422faed83059f3a88999cafe51